/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/image001.jpg" width="152" height="179"/></p> <p style="text-align: left;">Few acts are more romantic than baking a cake for the one you love. The only way to make this more heartfelt is to make hearts. The Heart Cake mould from <a href="//www.justmustard.com/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.justmustard.com']);" target="_blank">Mustard</a> cleverly allows you to bake 6 heart shaped cakes at once. This is also great if you happen to love six different people – though you might have to check local legislation first to make sure that’s allowed.</p> <p style="text-align: left;">We have one of these amazing cake moulds to give away worth a whopping £15.00, to grab yourself a chance of winning simply enter in the usual way using the Rafflecopter Widget below, enter as many times as you like and increase your chances on a daily basis, remember you need to be in it to win it!</p> <p style="text-align: left;">Watch out for future posts in which we&#8217;re going to put the &#8216;I Heart Cake&#8217; Mould to the test!!</p> <p><a class="rafl" id="rc-1c41675" href="//www.rafflecopter.com/rafl/display/1c41675/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','http://www.rafflecopter.com']);" rel="nofollow">a Rafflecopter giveaway</a><br/> <script type="text/javascript" src="//d12vno17mo87cx.cloudfront.net/embed/rafl/cptr.js"></script></p> <div class='yarpp-related'> <h3>You might also like:</h3> <div class="yarpp-thumbnails-horizontal"> <a class='yarpp-thumbnail' href="/la-cafetieres/" title='La Cafetière &#8211; Giveaway!!'> <img width="120" height="120" src="/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/la-cafetiere_master_logo-002-120x120.jpg" class="attachment-yarpp-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la cafetiere_master_logo-002"/><span class="yarpp-thumbnail-title">La Cafetière &#8211; Giveaway!!</span></a> <a class='yarpp-thumbnail' href="/measuring-jug/" title='Giveaway &#8211; Digital Scales Measuring Jug'